{"tid":1223632,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"希望大家準備遊行之餘，記一記住呢隻歌","createTime":"2019-06-14T18:03:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T18:19:00.000Z","uid":134134,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3413acbec3ecab23174f9d1ba2cd9fd7d86ab126","tid":1223632,"uid":134134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T18:03:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RNbXLbHrMds\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRNbXLbHrMds&d=YB8lrFeyQ%2BkzHCEHpdql8Kd04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=da7e8651\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RNbXLbHrMds</a><br />\n試問誰還未發聲<br />\n都捨我其誰衛我城<br />\n天生有權還有心可作主<br />\n誰要認命噤聲<br />\n試問誰能未覺醒<br />\n聽真那自由在奏鳴<br />\n激起再難違背的那份良知和應<br />\n<br />\n為何美夢仍是個夢 還想等恩賜泡影<br />\n為這黑與白這非與是 真與偽來做證<br />\n為這世代有未來 要及時擦亮眼睛<br />\n<br />\n無人有權沉默 看著萬家燈火變了色<br />\n問我心再用我手 去為選我命途力拼<br />\n人既是人 有責任有自由決定遠景<br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好睇少一首歌，歌曲可以做到嘅嘢係好多<br />\n你睇Sing Hallelujah to the Lord 就知<br />\n除咗可以好有效make a noise 之外，亦可以令人從心底發出共鳴<br />\n另外，我諗大家都知道<br />\n16號食清湯<br />\n17號食大辣<br />\n希望鍾意食辣嘅人唔好指責人食清湯咁廢，因為唔係人人食得辣<br />\n食清湯嘅人亦唔好介意人食得辣，因為佢哋都有食辣嘅原因<br />\n同枱食麵，互相遞下水，遞下筷子就好足夠<br />\n共勉之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"800b7da70ccc6abf4675f067d0836db0113eed4d","tid":1223632,"uid":43553,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T18:12:24.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e8f3116caf21dccd0bb3b5d9caddd64ea887883c","tid":1223632,"uid":134134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"800b7da70ccc6abf4675f067d0836db0113eed4d","tid":1223632,"uid":43553,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T18:12:24.000Z","msg":"Push"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T18:14:14.000Z","msg":"多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0476e0921b9f9a8474a3a62215762cdbb0330a0","tid":1223632,"uid":62373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T18:19:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}